@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Restaurants";
}

<div class="main-content">
    <h1>Recommended Restaurants</h1>
    <p>Here you can find a list of recommended restaurants in various popular destinations in Turkey.</p>

    <section>
        <h2>İstanbul</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Mikla Restaurant</h3>
            <img src="~/images/mikla-restoran-istanbul.jpg" alt="Mikla Restaurant">
            <p>Mikla Restaurant is one of Istanbul's most famous restaurants. It offers modern Turkish cuisine with a stunning view. Under the leadership of Chef Mehmet Gürs, Mikla provides an unforgettable dining experience with its creative dishes and panoramic views of Istanbul.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Kapadokya</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Seten Restaurant</h3>
            <img src="~/images/seten-restoran-kapadokya.jpg" alt="Seten Restaurant">
            <p>Seten Restaurant, located in the enchanting atmosphere of Cappadocia, offers traditional Turkish cuisine. It serves local flavors and authentic dishes of Cappadocia in a charming setting.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Antalya</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>7 Mehmet</h3>
            <img src="~/images/7-mehmet-restaurant-antalya.jpg" alt="7 Mehmet">
            <p>7 Mehmet is one of the most famous restaurants in Antalya. It offers the most delicious examples of Mediterranean cuisine. Known for its fresh seafood and regional dishes, this restaurant provides a perfect dining experience.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Pamukkale</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>White House Restaurant & Cafe</h3>
            <img src="~/images/white-house-restoran-pamukkale.jpg" alt="White House Restaurant & Cafe">
            <p>White House Restaurant & Cafe offers Turkish and international cuisine with a unique view of Pamukkale. This restaurant, with its warm and friendly atmosphere, provides visitors with an unforgettable dining experience.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Efes (Selçuk)</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Ejder Restaurant</h3>
            <img src="~/images/EjderRestaurant-efes.jpg" alt="Ejder Restaurant">
            <p>Ejder Restaurant is located near the ancient city of Ephesus and is famous for its traditional Turkish dishes. It offers guests authentic flavors and a historical atmosphere.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Bodrum</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Orfoz Restaurant</h3>
            <img src="~/images/orfoz-restoran-bodrum.jpg" alt="Orfoz Restaurant">
            <p>Orfoz Restaurant is one of the most popular seafood restaurants in Bodrum. Known for its fresh seafood and delicious Mediterranean cuisine, it offers a great dining experience by the sea.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Fethiye</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Mozaik Bahçe</h3>
            <img src="~/images/mozaikbahce-restoran-fethiye.jfif" alt="Mozaik Bahçe">
            <p>Mozaik Bahçe is a restaurant in Fethiye that offers authentic Turkish dishes. This restaurant, serving in an authentic garden setting, is known for its delicious food and relaxed atmosphere.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Çeşme</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Asma Yaprağı</h3>
            <img src="~/images/asmayapragi-cesme-restoran.jfif" alt="Asma Yaprağı">
            <p>Asma Yaprağı is a cozy and warm restaurant in Çeşme that offers delicious examples of Aegean cuisine. Known for its dishes prepared with fresh and local ingredients, it provides a delightful dining experience.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Trabzon</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Nihat Usta Akçaabat Köfte</h3>
            <img src="~/images/nihatusta-trabzon-restoran.jpg" alt="Nihat Usta Akçaabat Köfte">
            <p>Nihat Usta Akçaabat Köfte is a traditional and delicious restaurant where you can taste the famous Akçaabat meatballs of Trabzon. It is known for its regional dishes and friendly atmosphere.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>İzmir</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Deniz Restaurant</h3>
            <img src="~/images/denizrestoran-izmir.jpg" alt="Deniz Restaurant">
            <p>Deniz Restaurant, located on the famous Kordon in Izmir, is known for its fresh seafood and Aegean cuisine. It offers an unforgettable dining experience with a sea view.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

